ANALYSIS
This bill directs the department of health and human services to seek approval from Centers for
MedicareandMedicaidServicestocoverfamilycaregiversupportservicesasanallowableserviceunder
specified waiver programs. The bill also eliminates the child care scholarship cost share for children in
kinshipcare.
